## n8n@0.79.1 For a comprehensive list of changes, check out the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.79.0...n8n@0.79.1) for this version.
**Release date:** 2020-08-28 - Enhanced nodes - Contentful - HTTP Request - Postgres - Webhook - Removed Test-Webhook also in case checkExists fails - HTTP Request node doesn'toverwrite accept header if it's already set - Add rawBody to every request so that n8n doesn'tgive an error if body is missing
